3218. Crash Bandicoot (Fan Art)

Hope you all had a wonderful holiday! 

Here is a fanart of Crash Bandicoot :)

We have one week left for our limited edition Griffun plush Kick Starter campaign. To pre-order your own Griffun plush, check out the link in our IG bio or IG story.

#illustration #art #artist #cute # instagramartist #artistsoninstagram #crash #crashbandiccot #videogames #sony

Here are some highlights of my 2022 artwork. It's been an interesting year for us. My team and I decided to use The Apricat Plush to make our initial entry into the plush ecosystem. Thanks for all those who supported us. We're just about to complete fulfillment by delivering them along with the 2023 Calendars over the next couple of weeks.

We're also really close to finishing off our second plush campaign (The Snowy Griffún). If you'd like to pre-order your own, check out the link in our bio. Note, there are only 5 days left in the campaign so make your move now to lock one in.

2023 will bring with it more changes in the evolution of my artwork. We'll be starting a YouTube channel soon which will breathe additional life into my platform. The team and I are also working on a variety of exciting book and board game projects that'll debut once we wrap-up fulfillment on our current campaigns (stay-tuned for more info!)

Above all a BIG THANK YOU to all of you who've supported my artwork over the years. I and my team wish you all the best in the coming New Year! 🙂
